@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Landau Loyalty Rewards - FAQ";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Loyalty.cshtml";
}

<div class="row">
    <section class="faq">
        <h1>LOYALTY PROGRAM FAQ’s:</h1>
        <article>
            <h2>Can I earn Reward Points by just being a Loyalty Member?</h2>
            <p>In order to begin accumulating reward points you must first sign-up for the loyalty program through the link on the Landau brand’s website. Loyalty programs exist for all three of our Landau Family of Brands including: Landau Rewards, Urbane Rewards, and Smitten Entourage. Once you sign-up, you will have a unique log-in that includes your current information and points available. The loyalty program will track your future order activity and earned points to your profile page.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h2>How do I get a login?</h2>
            <p>After you register to become a Loyalty Member, you must sign-in to create a username from an existing email address and a password; an email confirmation will be sent along with a unique verification code to log into your profile page.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h2>How long does it take to get a password?</h2>
            <p>You will create your own password for the loyalty program.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h2>How are the points calculated?</h2>
            <p>Points are earned based on member engagements. The loyalty site has different “Journeys” that give you options to earn points. These include social and digital and social platforms including, but not limited to Facebook and Twitter, inviting a friend to the program, reviewing a product, and product purchase verification. Additional points will be offered on our social media sites or SMS through special promotions, contests, and sweepstakes. Points will only accumulate for Loyalty Members.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h2>What is the minimum number of points I need before I can redeem them for a reward?</h2>
            <p>The Loyalty Rewards Program is broken down into 3 tiers and Tier Levels will be based on points earned:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Silver: 50-275</li>
                <li>Gold: 276-500</li>
                <li>Platinum: 501-2000</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h2>Can I combine my points with other users or other loyalty programs?</h2>
            <p>Points are issued to each specific Loyalty Member. The landau Family of Brands has 3 different Loyalty Programs including: Landau Rewards, Urbane Rewards, and Smitten Entourage. Points are separate for each program and cannot be shared or combined across programs.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h2>What gifts are available?</h2>
            <p>Currently our loyalty sites are offering water bottles, grocery totes, note pads, bags, tumblers, jackets, shoes, and scrub sets, and many more items to Loyalty Members in our loyalty gift shop.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h2>When will I receive my gift?</h2>
            <p>All rewards are scheduled for delivery within 2 to 3 weeks of order placed based on availability.</p>
        </article>
    </section>
</div>









